Package: isoviz
Type: Package
Title: Visualize transcript isoforms alongside exon-exon junction counts
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Karin Isaev and Megan Schertzer
Maintainer: <kisaev@nygenome.org>
Description: Visualize which junctions are being utilized alongside annotated
    transcript isoforms. Find appropriate guide RNAs to target junction for 
    isoform specific knockdown. 
